# The Competence 🌐

A community platform connecting students across colleges in Tamil Nadu, enabling collaboration and knowledge sharing across domains like Full Stack, AI/ML, and UI/UX.

## 🚀 Features
- Domain-based community groups (Full Stack, AI/ML, UI/UX, etc.)
- Member profiles and connections
- Resource sharing and announcements
- Responsive, clean UI

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
React, Node.js, Express, MongoDB

